Info.Title: The Timber
Info.Writer: Steve Allrich, Anthony O'Brien, Colin Ossiander
Info.Actors: James Ransone, Elisa Lasowski, Mark Caven, William Gaunt
Info.Plot: In the wild west, two brothers embark on a journey to collect a bounty in a desperate attempt to save their home: but what they find along the way is more than they bargained for.
